{"tid":417021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人知地址 身分證佢有冇可能做到咩","createTime":"2017-09-28T09:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T13:51:06.000Z","uid":24869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"987a98f0211fcb2d71338cab42e9a165c1ab01a9","tid":417021,"uid":24869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"件事係咁既 <br />\n岩岩有個電話打過黎自稱某電訊公司<br />\n報出黎既plan都係正常價格（出街有見過）<br />\n登記資料果陣比左身分證number 地址<br />\n事後諗返好似唔多對路<br />\n上網搵一搵個電話<br />\n發現疑似係一個騙案電話<br />\n打返過去都係長響無人聽<br />\n所想問下各位只有以上資料可以拎黎做乜野<br />\n我都知我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 資料其實仲係我屋企人既（一向用佢個名上台）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該各位"},{"pid":"d18558e4ff855526b2077db01669d670398ac04a","tid":417021,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"報警先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600815ee23d3daa60f158e36f6be4153ea7fd9da","tid":417021,"uid":24869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ceb6888a60734f160783f23ba0975a1dcf4adc","tid":417021,"uid":135066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:48:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>報警先啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報咗先算"},{"pid":"d2927bd6d76047f7d0917e9d3eebe40cb2010984","tid":417021,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"